text: Silva Bendrāte (born February 29, 1956) is a Latvian radio journalist and politician, who served as deputy to the Latvian Saeima. == References == Category:1956 births Category:Living people Category:People from Kuldīga Category:New Era Party politicians Category:New Unity politicians Category:Deputies of the 8th Saeima Category:Deputies of the 9th Saeima Category:Deputies of the 10th Saeima Category:University of Latvia alumni Category:21st-century Latvian women politicians
